name: Fighter Being
description:
Fighter Being
Where there is magic, treasures, secrets, there should be battles too. To win a battle you need a party and that party needs a Fighter to stay in front. This Red Fighter Being is your front line and he trusts beings of the color red!

As a <red> being it can combine powers with other <red> beings. If the red beings win a fight - they get the loot drop for free.


Character from a live performance from Fireter - a theater of shadow and fire. 

Also a <red> <fighter> 
Original NFT from
www.fireter.com
